{"tid":1345262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非已經再冇撚用 727元朗見","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:08:14.000Z","uid":221351,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c37089b064e498aa012fe9d6d7c05505986184","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"警黑聯手 可以幫到手既只有自己人<br />\n727發夢要帶齊上戰場既裝備<br />\n已經冇得再回避/退後<br />\n比幫閪黑咁撚樣係西鐵站打<br />\n我地夠人既 已經可以收撚哂佢地夠<br />\n727發夢果日大家記得帶岩架生<br />\n戰場黎 唔係遊樂場<br />\n而家講緊既係夢中殺人<br />\n琴晚睇朗屏live已經睇得出香港係唔夠料<br />\n一啲都唔夠勇武<br />\n唔係想踩佢地 但事實真係咁<br />\n<br />\n727需要既係戰士"},{"pid":"1676e73549f081301b2747f5226fab0e707f31e4","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab6f3ff12328abba682ad64132dedfe2b57ef04e","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9796c88e648cfc1e7482b72f59aa1643c123550b","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78d68f1141078fae05f6e510011ee299f5f93f51","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"451fb5c379b66da85ae59e487663abf8d250a50a","tid":1345262,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n721元朗事件係恐怖襲擊，元朗圍村佬係恐怖分子，要有共識，要全部人知道。"},{"pid":"349203c0e755480b34b3fc0bc5305b12c3849f75","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n講得岩 只有香港人先咁撚樣忍得<br />\n而家直頭係有組織既恐怖份子打市民<br />\n根本冇可能忍到<br />\n727見"},{"pid":"384cd6805a0f276326a964dadc2e702d45c43ba1","tid":1345262,"uid":221351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"推 如果727都唔郁手 你班廢柴塞返入老母個閪到啦 我地人多既 做大佢 已經夠殺"},{"pid":"efbfc9ed054f8ef8aa5e259d4